									<div class="summary">
						<p>The <code>Auth</code> class handles HTTP Authentication encoding and decoding. Typically, this class is
not used directly, but is a utility of <code>net\http\Request</code>, <code>net\http\Response</code>, and
<code>security\auth\adapter\Http</code></p>
